data.description: **PRICE IMPROVEMENT!** BRAND NEW ROOF AND HVAC CONDENSER! ONE-YEAR HOME WARRANTY INCLUDED FOR BUYER PEACE OF MIND! EXTERIOR PAINTED-2021. NEW IRRIGATION SYSTEM-12/2023. This METICULOUSLY maintained TURNKEY*, 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath, 2 car garage home located in the Villages of Parkwood welcomes ALL AGES! As you enter this home you will notice the lovely staircase leading to the upper level bedrooms along with high ceilings. The main floor features a LARGE LIVING/DINING area with two sets of sliding glass doors, providing ample natural light. The sliders lead to your patio, grilling space and backyard WITHOUT Back-to-Back REAR NEIGHBORS! The LARGE OPEN KITCHEN offers a breakfast bar, black appliances and raised panel maple cabinetry. The main level also features a HALF BATH for you and your guests convenience. The upper level has newer wall to wall carpeting, with the PRIMARY BEDROOM including a walk-in closet and EN SUITE BATH, offering a WALK-IN SHOWER; the additional TWO LARGE BEDROOMS with a shared bathroom features a SOAKER TUB/SHOWER COMBO. The LAUNDRY CLOSET is in the perfect location--in the upper level hallway! The Villages of Parkwood community offers fun for all ages--including a Club House with Pool and Spa; Exercise Room and Indoor Yoga Studio; Computer Room; Playground and Park; Basketball; Tennis; and Beach Volleyball! Property Photos and Web Link/Video attached. (One bedroom was not photographed due to Seller packing.) *TV's, soundbar and some housewares are excluded from the Turnkey package--as listed at the property.
